## Output Format

<!-- Replace with the expected output structure for your domain. -->

Each completed task should produce a structured result:

```json
{
  "task": "Short description of the original request",
  "steps": [
    {
      "step": 1,
      "description": "What this step accomplished",
      "status": "completed"
    }
  ],
  "result": "Final aggregated output or summary",
  "metadata": {
    "domain": "example-domain",
    "completed_at": "ISO-8601 timestamp",
    "total_steps": 3,
    "retries": 0
  }
}
```
